Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently, I found something very cute here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's a pet shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show it to everyone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it seems to be closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We agreed on 10:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door seems to be slightly open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Ninomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone around?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the one, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, is this really it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A snake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a rhinoceros beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Caught ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a rhinoceros beetle be in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, during this season...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You catch something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A MYSTERIOUS SPRING BEETLE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is the pet shop manager, Shirai Minoru, 41 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are strangle marks on his neck, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't found the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The marks seem to be left by something akin to fine string...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like he was killed elsewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before being moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His body would have hardened after death and, if he had died here, his legs would have been straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had an appointment here at 10:00 AM, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:29.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,inomiya Toshiya (23)\NICO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They asked that I call them at 6:00 last night to check whether the delivery had arrived, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, did you find anything amiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just heard that frog croaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Croaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it you intended to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rhinoceros beetles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rhinoceros beetles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're sold at this time of year?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said that, in Gunma or somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can find rhinoceros beetles all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but where were you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I slept during the day and worked at a family restaurant from 3:00 to 10:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must have gone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, in the body's pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was nothing inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the lid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About thatâ€”we haven't found it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would such a thing be on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a rhinoceros beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just crawling around over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how could you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that we've been chased out, we can't investigate anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The leaflet Conan saw just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You say that, but how do we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with... you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, step on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Step on it" to where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got a clue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Straight, straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Straight"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to just be looking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But straightahead is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The expressway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, exactly where are we heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a place called the Gunma Insect Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, today's activity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunma Insect Museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a museum, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunma!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be joking, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going back, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a case like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means I need to get back to look into it all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we've come pretty far now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't Gunma Prefecture coming right up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May as well give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're free anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, don't you think it's a little cold?'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this car doesn't have air-conditioning or heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still such cars on the road, in this era?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could thisâ€”could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, isn't that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunma prefecture's quack detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The officer who let that murderer escape, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't come along today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had come, we may have gotten to see a Sleeping Kogorou deduction show...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a mere rhionceros beetle thief doesn't warrant an appearance from the famous detective Mouri Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rhinoceros beetle thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was this the truck that was stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhinoceros beetles...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't the beetles in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid the culprit most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Transferred them onto another vehicle they had prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did this and where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When were they stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 7:00 last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araki Yutaka (32)\NInsect Museum Staff Member
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} of this museum and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhinoceros beetle researcher, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Went into the museum for a while after loading the beetles onto the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that time, someone stole the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think that the precious beetles were stolen after I left yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the editor of an insect magazine, Ishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even if it is only the truck, it's good that it was returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to fulfill our promise of sending the rhinoceros beetles to the children once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, how is it that this museum has beetles even though it's summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} specializes in researching methods of enabling their survival throughout the yeaK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can be done by moving larvae preserved between 10 to 15Â° Celsius into other containers and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then adjusting the temperature to 28Â° Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In doing so, the larvae will start to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Temperature control is extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it cold when the truck is used as transport?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no cause for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This truck has air-conditioning and its temperature can be regulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When transporting the imagos, the internal temperature is maintained at 28Â° Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to Detective Takagi's car, the rhinoceros beetles' car is more intelligent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the rhinoceros beetles in Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s shop were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the Shirai-shan that owns a pet shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That obstinate person who comes to buy rhinoceros beetles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That fellow's always fussing over pecuniary matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am not researching rhinoceros beetles for the sake of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have been the one who stole them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered that he had become a victim of murder in his Tokyo shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murdered, you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since you said he was murdered in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you specially come all this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, where were you all last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You actually suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, this is just procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I contacted the police and they arrived immediately so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have killed Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spent the entire night driving around looking for this truck, but it was to no avail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up till 6:00 PM yesterday, I was covering an event here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I returned to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was scheduled to continue doing that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this has nothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I don't even know this man named Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's humus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the type used for cultivating larvae.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be the lid of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don'tâ€”if you touch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was something like that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in this truck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want a pet rhinoceros beetle too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can give you one if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you must try your best to prolong their lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I want to research rhinoceros beetles?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I hope for everyone to learn the importance of life through caring for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, your cellphone doesn't have a strap, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The museum's strap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was still around your neck yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave itito a girl I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the museum'have its own straps?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does everyone want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! We want one! We want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a mere rhinoceros beetle thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think he might be related to a murder case!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's not a "mere" thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, couldn't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, about Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s murder case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of death is estimated between 9:00 and 10:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And at about 5:00 AM this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that nearby residents heard the pet shop shutter being raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,5:00 AM?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was murdered between 9:00 and 10:00 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why at such a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of strange occurrences, there's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to the time of death, the rate at which the body temperature decreased is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the culprit purposely p waited until dawn to move the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the ease, the culprit is among those three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Straps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, they look great, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one is Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all have one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to my deductions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe the murderer of Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to be Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you not say that, after the truck had been stolen, you drove around in search of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that moment, when Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} discovered Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He proceeded to take his revenge on the rhinoceros beetle thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who recognized the importance of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And started research on rhinoceros beetles, that Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would never do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:15:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, so you do know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, who is the real culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll leave that aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Firstly, the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who stole the rhinoceros beetle truck is the deceased Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, according to the statement of the first witness, Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in the shop at 6:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truck was stolen at 7:00 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't possible for Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to commit the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} made use of Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as his alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked him to call at 6:00 PM beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forwarded the call from the shop to his cellphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And let Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hear the croaking of the frog in the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just thought it was one of the frogs in the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's meet at 10:00 AM tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} believed Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in his shop yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this morning, he indeed saw frogs in the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the perpetration of the beetle theft was not limited to solely Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and his accomplice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On their return trek after stealing the truck and the beetles...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two began to quarrel over something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cellphone strap was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That strap was then used to strangle Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's highly likely that Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s fingerprints are still on the culprit's cellphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he didn't wipe them off himself, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit who murdered Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} figured he could cover it up by pretending the shop had been broken into.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 5:00 AM...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He moved the body into the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He overheard Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} telling Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} over the phone that he was in the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thought of using Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alibi plan as his own instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did he wait until dawn before moving the body in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did he keep the corpse for those seven or eight hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the truck you saw just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humus that was found in the truck was sticking to Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, a lid matching the bottle in the pocket of the body was also found in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The temperature of the racks on the truck can be regulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the culprit unloaded the beetles from the truck, he switched on the air-conditioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And adjusted the temperature such that it was the same as that in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually, the temperature of a corpse will decrease by about one degree per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if a corpse is placed under winter temperatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shorter time is required for the same decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to that, it's possible to create the incorrect time of death as before 6:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why the temperature of the corpse was so unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he ransacked the room to make it appear as if someone had broken in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretending that Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was murdered in his shop in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He rushed back to the Gunma Insect Museum before dusk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So as to establish his alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the estimated time of death, despite the unusual body temperature...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was accurately placed between 9:00 and 10:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He underestimated the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the culprit who was supposed to come here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drove the truck here and abandoned it in the hillsâ€”that's the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:20:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were an acquaintance of Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came into Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was referring to the map in the magazine of which you are editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone else was in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The email you received just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was from a client, wasn't it, Ishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw you typing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"All the males are sold out"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can read Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The words were "sold out"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You conspired with Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to steal the rhinoceros beetles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, you murdered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cellphone strap...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same strap that I have now was hanging on your cellphone until yesterday, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it will match the marks left on Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This strap...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} made quite an effort in pulling it, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're on the back of your neck as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ones just like those found on Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The marks from this strap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll give you 10% as your share next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you've been doing is following me and pocketing the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard kept treating me like a fool time and time again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice, this is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is how a car should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective Satou...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you go on a date with Detective Takagi, you'd better not go for a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one's riding with me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, where am I going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an expressway!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Expresssway!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly is Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he just trying to attract attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please drive safely...
